dialogue.text: Can't you see you're hurting actual people? And for what? Just because you can?
A shame, a shame. But I cannot be the one to blame, blame!
All I did was play a game, game! Not my fault they couldn't keep the pace, pace!
Jevil, what happened to you? You've lost your mind ever since you've met that strange pers--
CAN IT, CAN IT!!! WHAT DO YOU KNOW ABOUT FREEDOM?!? NOTHING! NOTHING!
(sigh) This is about what I expected... Don't make this any harder than it needs to be.
A key, a key? Oh Seam, you really don't realize what you're doing to them.
Get in the cell, I don't wanna hurt you.
NU-HAH! NAY, NAY I SAY!\nNot without one last game, game!
Uee hee hee hee! Let the games begin!
After all, 'tis but THE TRUE AND NEO CHAOS! NU-HAH HAH HAH!
Jevil's nonsense will cause confusion, spinning your notes around and summoning distractions. Stay focused!
